* Biomass looked around with his huget eyes as the sun got so that it wasn't 
so blinding, but that was the first time he'd been above water so it was 
only expected.
Nue'e blinked and tired to see what was on the island close to them because 
her scanners were detecting a few of those beings they were sent to study.
There was a really big male there and a female?
With one of her little fins she tugged on a tenticle.*

" There's beings on the shore."

* Biomass looked towards the shore and studied the robotic people there, 
swimming towards them a little until he stopps dead at Perndabots quick 
mevement, drawing a weapon and aiming it towards him.
Biomass sucks his tenticles in at the surprise of it all, having a rather 
funny look on his face for a shocked squid.*

" Um...I am Biomass..." he gestured towards himself with a long tenticle, 
then gesturing towards Nue'e.*
" This is Nue'e, my biologist."

* Biomass moved towards land more, his tenticles long enough that by the 
time he was moving in 12 ft of water his tenticles were streatched out and 
probing the shore of the beach he was approaching, one getting really close 
to Perndabot and a few more snaking around Swift's feet.
Biomass made it to the beack and discovered that Perndabot didn't seem so 
big now that he was up close.
Nue'e swam as close to the shore as she could without beaching herself, 
transforming into robot mode and walking the rest of the way. Stopping 
beside Biomass and clasping her hands infront of her hips. Then moving to 
shove her glasses up the bridge of her nose.*
